# ============================================================
# LOCATION DETAIL OPERATIONS
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: operations
domain: detail
subdomain: location-detail
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

purpose:
Defines operational handling for location detail.

scope:
Covers zone-detail publication, restricted-area review,
historical layout inspection, and closure handling.

required_behavior:
- Support zone-detail publication.
- Support restricted-area review.
- Support historical layout inspection.
- Support closure and reopening review.
- Support containment for unsafe zone disclosure.

state_model:
location_detail_operational_state:
- prepared
- reviewed
- active
- restricted
- closed
- archived
- contained

validation_rules:
- location_ref is required.
- zone scope must be valid.
- restricted or closed zones must not be published as open.
- historical layouts must preserve effective period boundaries.

transition_rules:
- prepared -> reviewed
- reviewed -> active
- active -> restricted
- restricted -> closed
- active -> archived
- active -> contained
- contained -> restricted
- closed -> archived

operational_focus:
- zone updates
- access-scope review
- closed-zone archival handling
- historical layout inspection

failure_codes:
- LOCATION_DETAIL_OP_REF_MISSING
- LOCATION_DETAIL_OP_ZONE_INVALID
- LOCATION_DETAIL_OP_SCOPE_CONFLICT
- LOCATION_DETAIL_OP_HISTORICAL_PERIOD_INVALID
